<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>We value your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our Customer Feedback Portal.</p>

<h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
<p>When you use our portal, we may collect the following types of information:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number (if provided).</li>
    <li><strong>Feedback Content:</strong> Comments, ratings, suggestions, and any other information you submit.</li>
    <li><strong>Technical Data:</strong> IP address, browser type, device information, and usage data.</li>
</ul>

<h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
<p>We use the information you provide to:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Understand and improve our products and services.</li>
    <li>Respond to your feedback or inquiries.</li>
    <li>Analyze trends and customer satisfaction.</li>
    <li>Ensure the security and functionality of the portal.</li>
</ul>

<h2>3. Sharing Your Information</h2>
<p>We do <strong>not sell</strong> your personal information. We may share your information only with:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Internal teams responsible for customer service and product improvement.</li>
    <li>Trusted service providers who help us operate the portal (e.g., hosting, analytics), under strict confidentiality agreements.</li>
    <li>Legal authorities if required to comply with law or protect our rights.</li>
</ul>

<h2>4. Data Security</h2>
<p>We take appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction.</p>

<h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
<p>We retain your feedback and associated personal information only as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes stated above, or as required by law.</p>

<h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
<p>You have the right to:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Request access to the data we hold about you.</li>
    <li>Request correction or deletion of your personal information.</li>
    <li>Withdraw your consent at any time (where applicable).</li>
</ul>
<p>To exercise these rights, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@example.com">support@gmail.com</a>.</p>

<h2>7. Use of Cookies</h2>
<p>We may use cookies or similar technologies to enhance user experience and collect analytics. You can manage cookie preferences through your browser settings.</p>

<h2>8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
<p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date.</p>

